<thing name="Binding" descriptors="xworker.lang.MetaDescriptor3">
    <description><![CDATA[<p>A&nbsp;Binding&nbsp;calculates a value that depends on one or more sources. The sources are usually called the dependency of a binding. A binding observes its dependencies for changes and updates its value automatically.</p>
]]></description>
